"title": "8166: theology",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8166: theology",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The study of God, as he has revealed himself in Jesus Christ and in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Theology is based on God's self-revelation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:15–3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1-Rom1:3\">ROM 1:1–1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1-1Cor15:4\">1CO 15:1–15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a></p>\n<h2>The benefits of theology</h2>\n<h3>A concern for right teaching in the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:1\">TIT 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1-Heb6:3\">HEB 6:1–6:3</a></p>\n<h3>A deepened understanding of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:169\">PSA 119:169</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:24\">PSA 119:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14-2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:14–3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual illumination</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:8\">1JN 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Access to the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4\">PSA 33:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:43\">PSA 119:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:160\">PSA 119:160</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:3-Col1:6\">COL 1:3–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:5\">REV 21:5</a></p>\n<h3>An inspiration to meditation and praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:15-Ps119:16\">PSA 119:15–119:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:9\">PSA 48:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:4\">PSA 56:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:10\">PSA 56:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97-Ps119:98\">PSA 119:97–119:98</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:148\">PSA 119:148</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:5\">PSA 143:5</a></p>\n<h3>A life of obedience and holiness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9-Ps119:11\">PSA 119:9–119:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22\">JAS 1:22</a></p>",
